column1: Added support for Android tombstoning . Made Game static . Made Paused eventhandler static . Have OnCreate set window NoTitle . Have OnPause set resourceslost flag and Unbind View . Have OnResume grab window and reinitialize GraphicsDevice . Added pause and resume for mediaplayer when activity is paused or resumed . Fix disposing of Android textures . Added a global list that will create OpenGL textures on the next draw . This is to prevent random pauses in the game play . Added reloading support for textures . Added capability to force fullscreen to be reset . Added static list of content managers that have been created so that on restore of the application , each content manager can restore textures .

column1: AsyncEnumerable . ToObservable : Do not call IAsyncEnumerator < T > . MoveNext with an already canceled CancellationToken . This would happen whenever an IObserver < T > . OnNext would dispose its subscription within a call to OnNext . The built in AnonymousAsyncEnumerator < T > checks whether it ' s already disposed , however , not every user code might handle canceled tokens that gracefully . Also , the continuation of MoveNext will not scheduled anyway .
